    "name": "Tabletop Tavern",
    "steam_appid": 3337380,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337380/extras/ef363c9a6dbac442e1ae17040cce3714.poster.avif?t=1772024668\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337380/extras/ef363c9a6dbac442e1ae17040cce3714.webm?t=1772024668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337380/extras/ef363c9a6dbac442e1ae17040cce3714.mp4?t=1772024668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在紧张激烈的实时战斗中指挥你的军队，站位、时机与协同将决定胜负。组建纪律严明的长矛阵对抗骑兵，保护弓箭手免受侧翼突袭，并利用地形取得优势。沼泽、森林、丘陵与河道关卡将深刻影响战斗节奏与局势走向。从小规模遭遇战到屏幕上数百单位的宏大战役，每一场战斗都考验你的战略本能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337380/extras/c61da86145641ad38136fd399b2e5424.poster.avif?t=1772024668\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337380/extras/c61da86145641ad38136fd399b2e5424.webm?t=1772024668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337380/extras/c61da86145641ad38136fd399b2e5424.mp4?t=1772024668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Tabletop Tavern 的 roguelike 战役每一次都是全新冒险，迫使你不断适应与进化。招募新单位，发现稀有装备，解锁永久改变策略的强化。随着难度递增、随机事件与数十位可解锁英雄与阵营，没有两次战役会完全相同。每次游玩都带来新的挑战与机会，需要谨慎决策才能铸就胜利并掌控战场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337380/extras/1e1f8844e5b290053cdd8f25af6af780.poster.avif?t=1772024668\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337380/extras/1e1f8844e5b290053cdd8f25af6af780.webm?t=1772024668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337380/extras/1e1f8844e5b290053cdd8f25af6af780.mp4?t=1772024668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>指挥各具特色的阵营，每个阵营都拥有独特玩法。率领维京精锐步兵、兽人阵营的巨魔与巨人、敏捷华丽的精灵、坚韧的人类、顽强的矮人等更多势力。每个阵营都拥有改变军队构筑方式的英雄能力，帮助你最大化部队战斗效率。打造军队不仅仅是数字堆叠，更是掌握阵营特色并建立符合你征服风格的协同组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337380/extras/1b6853123caac2bae510effc92c80cca.poster.avif?t=1772024668\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337380/extras/1b6853123caac2bae510effc92c80cca.webm?t=1772024668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337380/extras/1b6853123caac2bae510effc92c80cca.mp4?t=1772024668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>招募并率领一群仿佛从托尔金小说中走出的雇佣兵。维京狂战士、精灵弓手、人类骑士、矮人火炮等众多单位等待你的指挥。战斗在桌面风格战场上展开，每一次交锋都如同实时呈现的微缩战争游戏。战斗之间，你将管理军队、面对艰难抉择，并通过战略决策塑造战役走向。凭借无限协同、严酷选择与极高重玩性，Tabletop Tavern 将 RTS 的深度与 roguelike 的沉浸感完美融合。</p>",
